{"tid":2116650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部： 英國以國家安全為藉口  打壓 華為","createTime":"2020-07-20T09:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T10:20:52.000Z","uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a57d64d504a87cfd1453cebcc7077fcd1e14f005","tid":2116650,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:48:08.000Z","msg":"英據報尋求日本助建5G　外交部：反對藉國安打壓企業<br />\n<br />\n對於有日本傳媒報道，英國排除華為在5G建設後，尋求日本協助建立5G網絡；在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌回應，反對在沒有任何事實根據和確鑿證據的情況下，違背市場規律和公平競爭原則，排斥特定國家的特定企業，甚至藉口國家安全，不擇手段打壓外國企業，人為阻隔合作。這樣做只會損害自身利益和信譽，阻礙全人類的發展和進步。<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-20 15:58:40 (1)<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538848-20200720.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538848-20200720.htm&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=f01ca823\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538848-20200720.htm&h=d23b4402\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538848-20200720.htm</a>"},{"pid":"440503003249c874bd7e4d59ddfb9fcd79ebf2bd","tid":2116650,"uid":5674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:51:00.000Z","msg":"反對藉國安 打壓社會聲音"},{"pid":"788aa5e7687a96c1b1d1e8f9faddc5545599f5ef","tid":2116650,"uid":63406,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"中國以國家安全為由<br />\n打擊香港人自由"},{"pid":"b823e516171f1109c66e853b0bb043f57aa3eac0","tid":2116650,"uid":20362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:53:32.000Z","msg":"直頭唔比上google fb 又點計"},{"pid":"e47a2b13616bb8b7d97a1077ab566710db5b643b","tid":2116650,"uid":11082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b823e516171f1109c66e853b0bb043f57aa3eac0","tid":2116650,"uid":20362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:53:32.000Z","msg":"直頭唔比上google fb 又點計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:56:23